n doesn’t cause permanents you tap for mana to produce one extra mana — rather, it doubles the type and amount of mana that permanent would produce. For example, if you tap Mystic Gate for {W}{U}, it will produce {W}{W}{U}{U} instead.£5/1/2008: The effects of multiple Mana Reflections are cumulative. For example, if you have three Mana Reflections on the battlefield, you’ll get eight times the original amount and type of mana.£5/1/2008: If you have Mana Reflection on the battlefield and tap a permanent for mana, but another replacement effect would change the type and/or amount of mana it would produce (such as Contamination, which says “If a land is tapped for mana, it produces {B} instead of any other type and amount”), you decide what order to apply those effects in. In this example, applying Mana Reflection first and Contamination second would result in {B}; applying Contamination first and Mana Reflection second would result in {B}{B}.','G',NULL,'25.49','31.04','35.89',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','魔力映象','Mana Reflection','Réverbération de mana','Manaspiegelung','Riflesso di Mana','マナの反射','Reflexo de Mana','Отражение Маны','Reflejo de maná',NULL,'结界','Enchantment','Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント','Encantamento','Чары','Encantamiento',NULL,'如果你横置任一永久物来产生法术力，则改为它产生两倍的该类法术力。','If you tap a permanent for mana, it produces twice as much of that mana instead.','Si vous engagez un permanent pour du mana, il produit deux fois cette quantité de mana à la place.','Falls du eine bleibende Karte für Mana tappst, erzeugt sie stattdessen das Doppelte dieses Manas.','Se TAPpi un permanente per attingere mana, produce invece il doppio di quel mana.','あなたがマナを生み出す目的でパーマネントをタップする場合、代わりにそれはその２倍のマナを生み出す。','Se você virar uma permanente para gerar mana, em vez disso, ela produzirá o dobro daquela quantidade de mana.','Если вы поворачиваете перманент для получения маны, он производит вдвое больше той маны вместо этого.','Si giras un permanente para obtener maná, en vez 