r types.','#_In times of portent, the land sculpts itself in accordance with the sigils burned on the sky._#',NULL,'John Avon','126','4.175','£5/1/2008: Each land you control will have the land types Plains, Island, Swamp, Mountain, and Forest. They’ll also have the mana ability of each basic land type (for example, Forests can tap to produce {G}). They’ll still have their other subtypes and abilities.£5/1/2008: Giving a land extra basic land types doesn’t change its name or whether it’s legendary or basic.','G',NULL,'23.89','27.86','37.94',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'G','五彩预兆','Prismatic Omen','Augure prismatique','Prismatisches Omen','Presagio Prismatico','虹色の前兆','Agouro Prismático','Призматическое Знамение','Presagio prismático',NULL,'结界','Enchantment','Enchantement','Verzauberung','Incantesimo','エンチャント','Encantamento','Чары','Encantamiento',NULL,'由你操控的地均额外具有所有基本地类别。','Lands you control are every basic land type in addition to their other types.','Les terrains que vous contrôlez ont chaque type de terrain de base en plus de leurs autres types de terrain.','Länder, die du kontrollierst, haben zusätzlich zu ihren anderen Typen alle Standardlandtypen.','Le terre che controlli hanno tutti i tipi di terra base in aggiunta ai loro altri tipi.','あなたがコントロールする土地は、それ自身のタイプに加えてすべての基本土地タイプでもある。','Os terrenos que você controla são de todos os tipos de terreno básico além de seus outros tipos.','Земли под вашим контролем обладают всеми типами базовых земель в дополнение к своим другим типам.','Las tierras que controlas son de todos los tipos de tierra básica además de sus otros tipos.',NULL,'#_在预兆之时，大地将依照天空燃烧的印记形状来型塑自身。_#','#_In times of portent, the land sculpts itself in accordance with the sigils burned on the sky._#','#_Dans les temps de présage, la terre se sculpte en fonction des sigles marquant le ciel._#','#_In Zeiten von Omen verändert sich das Land passend zu den Siegeln, die brennend am Himmel erscheinen._#','#_In tempi di prodigi, la terra si scolpisce secondo i sigilli marchiati a fuoco nel cielo._#','#_兆しの時、その地は空に炎で刻まれた紋章を自身に刻んだ。_#','#_Nos momentos de presságio, a terra se esculpe de acordo com os símbolos que ardem nos céus._#','#_Когда случается предзнаменование, земля принимает форму запечатленных на небе знаков._#','#_En tiempos de adversidad, la tierra toma su forma de acuerdo a los signos que arden en el cielo._#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('154402','Prismwake Merrow','SHM','Creature — Merfolk Wizard','C','{2}{U}','3','2','1',NULL,'Flash£When Prismwake Merrow enters the battlefield, target permanent becomes the color or colors of your choice until end of turn.','#_"Seeing is believing" is a fact the merrows ruthlessly exploit in their dealings with the other residents of Shadowmoor._#',NULL,'Wayne England','46','2.111','£5/1/2008: An effect that changes a permanent’s colors overwrites all its old colors unless it specifically says “in addition to its other colors.” For example, after Cerulean Wisps resolves, the affected creature will just be blue. It doesn’t matter what colors it used to be (even if, for example, it used to be blue and black).£5/1/2008: Changing a permanent’s color won’t change its text. If you turn Wilt-Leaf Liege blue, it will still affect green creatures and white creatures.£5/1/2008: Colorless is not a color.£5/1/2008: You can choose any single color or any combination of more than one color. You can’t choose colorless.£5/1/2008: This ability won’t make an artifact stop being an artifact. It’ll just be a colorful artifact.','U',NULL,'0.01','0.17','1.37',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'U','彩迹美洛','Prismwake Merrow','Suire au sillage prismatique','Prismensog-Merrow','Merrow dalla Scia Prismatica','虹跡のメロウ','Sirenídeo Rastro-Prísmeo','Мерроу Радужного Следа','Merrow estela prismática',NULL,'生物～人鱼／法术师','Creature — Merfolk Wizard','Créature : ondin et sorcier','Kreatur — Meervolk, Zauberer','Creatura — Mago Tritone','クリーチャー ― マーフォーク・ウィザード','Criatura — Tritão Mago','Существо — Мерф